fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator

Class EndpointResolverGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.AbstractGenerator
      • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.EndpointResolverGenerator

  • public class EndpointResolverGenerator
extends AbstractGenerator
    AbstractGenerator implementation for generating LighterRequestResolver implementations. This generator does the bulk of the code generation work in lighter-compiler. Because of this, internally it uses the components from fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint to separate code generation responsibilities. In order to understand how this class works, it is important to understand how all those classes work. This class also makes use of the fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.codegen tools extensively.
